channel.title: Project Rebirth
channel.description:
Hello and welcome to the offical Project Rebirth thread. This project is a 718/742 revision, and when finished every skill will be trainable and hopefully 100%. I know some of the skills are a little tougher, however with time and hard work this goal may come to life. This project is currently the brainchild of two developers, however we hope to attract 2 more devolpers through this thread, and possibly even a web developer. We are working mainly at night, however recently I've begun to code throughout the day as well. Anyways without further delay lets get to it.
Green=Done, Yellow currently started, red not started.
Goals Runecrafting alters done Runespan Fully working abyss (done except for repair mage) Slayer Master with dialouge All Minigames working 100% (currently about 30%) All items cookable (bread,pie,cake etc) Construction Dungeoneering Troll invasion All magic spells (ancient,lunar,modern) Barbarian Firemaking All agility arenas (currently have wilderness agility arena added) alot more, ill add as it devolp it.
Devolpers Steven Jonathon Open Open
Images [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/34shz6c.png[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/9qco6c.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2eeeanq.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/15mlahe.png[/img]
Thanks for taking the time to read this. Have a great day
